class string{
public static void main(String[] args){
String s1="Good Morning";
System.out.println(s1);
System.out.println("To upper case:"+s1.toUpperCase());
System.out.println("\n To lower case:"+s1.toLowerCase());
}
}

-----output-----
mlm@mlm-ThinkCentre-E73:~/Desktop/java$ java string.java
Good Morning
To upper case:GOOD MORNING

 To lower case:good morning

